            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I would like to extend my heartfelt gratitude to the entire team at EuroKids Viman Nagar—from the Principal to the teachers and all the support staff—for nurturing my child so wonderfully during his Preschool and Day Care journey.\n\nMy son has recently completed his Nursery and Jr. KG here, and I am truly impressed with the quality of learning and the emphasis on creativity. The beautiful crafts he brought home over the years have now become cherished decorations in our living room.\n\nHe also attended Day Care after school, and throughout these two years, I never had a single concern or complaint. Everything has been managed with great care and professionalism, and I am extremely satisfied with the overall experience.\n\nAs a working professional with frequent outstation travel, I was initially worried about being able to spend enough time teaching him basic concepts like ABCs and numbers. However, thanks to the dedication and efforts of his teachers, he has learned everything so well that I never had to worry.\n\nI will always be grateful to EuroKids Viman Nagar for the love, care, and strong foundation they have provided to my child. Thank you for everything!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
