          "datePublished": "2024-09-05",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Dearest Reshma ma’am & Nursery class teachers ma’am’s\n\nA very Happy Teachers’ Day to all of you!\n\nYou are Darsha’s superhero’s in school, we cannot thank you enough for the care, support & knowledge you impart to Darsha, makes us feel extremely privileged to have our child study in EuroKids, Vimannagar Campus under the able leadership of Ms. Reshma ma’am. Thank you ma’am!\n\nAlso, the Nursery class teachers Shabnam ma’am & Radhika ma’am are the best any child as young as 3.5 can get exposed to . We see each day the effort and meticulous care given by them!\n\nDarsha has undoubtedly showing improvements with the time she is spending in class!\n\nWe as parents wish you all the best always! Thank you for empowering our child Darsha 🩷 🙏\n\nThe Best Pre-school branch in entire Pune. We have visited many schools prior to getting our child enrolled here - but nothing can be compared to EuroKids, Vimannagar Branch. Thank You!!\n\nDipsikha & Seethal Mishra ( Darsha’s Parents )\nNursery batch ( 2024-25)",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
